# NOKTA ACADEMY MANAGEMENT SYSTEM - COMPLETE DOCUMENTATION

## PROJECT OVERVIEW
Nokta Academy Management System - Full-Stack JavaScript/TypeScript application with React 18 frontend, Node.js/Express backend, MongoDB database. Production-ready with PWA offline support.

## TECH STACK
Frontend: React 18, Vite, Tailwind CSS, React Query, Zustand, React Router DOM, i18next, Framer Motion, Lucide Icons, Vite PWA Plugin
Backend: Node.js, Express.js, MongoDB, Mongoose, TypeScript, JWT, bcryptjs, Joi
Database: MongoDB with Mongoose ODM, auto-generated ObjectIds

## AUTHENTICATION & AUTHORIZATION
JWT Authentication with access/refresh tokens, bcryptjs password hashing. RBAC with 7 roles: super_admin, admin, teacher, student, family_student, accountant, librarian. API-level authorization middleware, protected routes.

## STATE MANAGEMENT
Zustand for global auth state, React Query for server state with caching, localStorage for persistent auth tokens.

## OFFLINE SUPPORT / PWA
Service Worker with cache-first strategy, Web App Manifest, offline navigation, auto-update. Backend seed script generates local profile images. Service worker caches /uploads/* images for offline display.

## PERFORMANCE OPTIMIZATION
Lazy loading (route-based and component-based), React.memo, bundle optimization, generic CRUD engine (single component handles all data operations), file count reduction from 100+ to ~30 files, API caching, debounced search.

